All i'm saying, is....<br>
<br>
<br>
When ever I tried to get in on a CoF....their whole beef was. &quot;bards can haste themselves, they don't need CoF&quot;.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
I don't give a shit about haste....bards have tons of haste items.<br>
<br>
<br>
BUT SO DO ALL THE OTHER MELEE'S!<br>
<br>
<br>
I mean, rogue epic....40%haste?...and correct me if i'm wrong, but isn't rogue epic easier than getting a CoF?<br>
<br>
Monk epic....same as rogue.<br>
<br>
And those types of hastes don't stack.<br>
<br>
<br>
I do notice a difference in speed change when I have lute of the howler on + eyepatch....as opposed to lute+eyepatch+epic.<br>
<br>
<br>
CoF on the other hand, is one of the nicest cloaks on the market &quot;pre&quot; ToV/Kael...for a bard. Nice stats, nice weight, and there's some haste on there to.<br>
<br>
I know I said before that when bards get epic, they hardly use their instruments ever again.<br>
<br>
Which is true...I never use my instruments now that I have epic.<br>
<br>
<br>
And yes, I do &quot;decent&quot; damage...highest damage output of 95pts in 1 swing.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
I'm to lazy to get the actual numbers of how much i do per fight, and I cannot say weather or not CoF would have any effect on my damage output as of now.<br>
<br>
<br>
I can say, that It would lighten my load, and increase my stats if I had a CoF over my cloak of Shadows.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
So to conclude....for pre, and post epic bards.....CoF is still a very nice item.<br>
<br>
It may not turn them into this mad killing machine, like everyone else seems to think it will to their class/character....but that person will be very happy with owning a CoF, and will most likely wear it until they obtain a better cloak....that is unless their a prick, and sell it right after the raid lol. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/unightgod.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NightGod</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/7/02 4:37:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=286.topic&index=46>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ...</span><hr size=1> &lt;== Gonna PL a bard to 47 just so he can roll on something on Naggy raids and have a decent excuse bitch if he doesn't get to roll.<br>
